text: Novonachalovsky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Nachalovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 808 as of 2010. There are 36 streets. == Geography == It is located 8 km from Astrakhan, 4 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Novonachalovsky
